name: One Night in Eternity
description:

One Night in Eternity 
Take a picture of a city under an ominous sky. Spend a day doing nothing as the world floats by.Meet a stranger, rise in love, spread your wings and soar through that heady feeling till your past seems a lie. Spend a day doing nothing, watching the world slowly die.
